comments: I did not notice any patterns and I tried to memorize the names without taking notes. Sometimes I tried to connect it to words I know to remember what letter the alienword starts with. For example the circle was called "wopee..." I tried to remember "w" like in "walking" by imagining walking in circles.. Other than that it was hard to remember the correct spelling. I tried to make connection based on the colors but it didn't work most of the time.
